{
  "texts": [
    "Internal Validity.",
    "Bias is one of the main concerns for internal validity.",
    "To mitigate bias, the experts in RQ2 had no exposure to our technical approach.",
    "Further, there was a possibility of social desirability bias, where experts might refrain from expressing dissenting opinions-we implemented several strategies to counteract this.",
    "We provided opportunities for each expert to voice their opinions, asked them to verbalize their rationales, and randomly alternated the sequence in which they reviewed the TSs."
  ]
}